examples.en: We copy instinctively the voices of our companions.
The instinctive reaction of a mother is to protect her children.
Fish instinctively fight their way upstream against the current.
Without conscious thought, she instinctively placed a hand on his arm.
We instinctively distrust those phone calls that tell us we have won a free vacation or car.
Cats have an instinctive desire to hunt.
